- [medium] src/views/dashboard/SuggestionsView.vue:354 (correctness): The direct suggestions route instantiates useDashboardSuggestions before the cached feature probe has completed. Those useDataApi calls are immediate, and the mounted hook still polls after fetchDashboardSuggestionsConfig without checking dashboardSuggestionsEnabled, so visiting /dashboards/suggestions/:sspId hits suggestion endpoints even when /api/dashboard-suggestions/config later says the feature is disabled or fails closed. That breaks the intended fail-closed gate and can show a broken suggestions workspace or generate 404/403 noise for a disabled feature.
- [medium] src/views/dashboard/partials/SuggestionScopeDialog.vue:151 (correctness): After generate returns a server ceiling error, canGenerate stays false because ceilingError remains set. The operator can change the selected controls or label sets, but this component never emits any scope-change or clear event, and the parent only clears scopeCeilingError at the start of generate, which is now disabled. The dialog can get stuck blocking every retry until the page is refreshed.
